What is compelling about this reality, and the reason I latched onto Zucker=
berg=E2=80=99s comments in that call, is that Meta is uniquely positioned t=
o overcome all of the limitations of open source, from training to verifica=
tion to RLHF to data quality, precisely because the company=E2=80=99s busin=
ess model doesn=E2=80=99t depend on having the best models, but simply on t=
he world having a lot of them.

